        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2129489999" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18279811982596710946">In style and structure, this made me think of <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/5544.Surely_You_re_Joking__Mr__Feynman__Adventures_of_a_Curious_Character' title='Surely You&apos;re Joking, Mr. Feynman! Adventures of a Curious Character by Richard Feynman' rel='nofollow noopener'> Surely You&apos;re Joking, Mr. Feynman</a>. People who are into this might dig Astra Taylor&apos;s <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13168201.The_People_s_Platform_Taking_Back_Power_and_Culture_in_the_Digital_Age' title='The People&apos;s Platform Taking Back Power and Culture in the Digital Age by Astra Taylor' rel='nofollow noopener'> The People&apos;s Platform</a> or her great essay <a href='https://thebaffler.com/salvos/serfing-the-net' rel='nofollow noopener'>&quot;Serfing the Net&quot;</a></span>
  <span id="freeText18279811982596710946" style="display:none">In style and structure, this made me think of <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/5544.Surely_You_re_Joking__Mr__Feynman__Adventures_of_a_Curious_Character" title="Surely You're Joking, Mr. Feynman! Adventures of a Curious Character by Richard Feynman" rel="nofollow noopener"> Surely You're Joking, Mr. Feynman</a>. People who are into this might dig Astra Taylor's <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13168201.The_People_s_Platform_Taking_Back_Power_and_Culture_in_the_Digital_Age" title="The People's Platform Taking Back Power and Culture in the Digital Age by Astra Taylor" rel="nofollow noopener"> The People's Platform</a> or her great essay <a href="https://thebaffler.com/salvos/serfing-the-net" rel="nofollow noopener">"Serfing the Net"</a></span>
