<li class='cover' id='bookCover_40180066'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/40180066-team-human"><img alt="Team Human" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1529062189l/40180066._SX98_.jpg" />
